title: Directs the department of agriculture and markets to inspect the condition of certain horse stalls in N.Y. city
summary: Directs the department of agriculture and markets to inspect the condition of certain horse stalls in cities with a population of one million or more.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the agriculture and markets law and the administrative code of the city of New York, in relation to the inspection of certain horse stables in cities of one million or more
